      • dump

        protected String dump(boolean canonical)
        已过时。 
        从类复制的说明: TemplateElement
        Brings the implementation of TemplateElement.getCanonicalForm() and TemplateElement.getDescription() to a single place. Don't call those methods in method on this, because that will result in infinite recursion!
        指定者:
        dump 在类中 TemplateElement
        参数:
        canonical - if true, it calculates the return value of TemplateElement.getCanonicalForm(), otherwise of TemplateElement.getDescription().
